{
  "stem": "23131.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because from the sight of the rest of the people, they tried to save themselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His big thing was that he tried to save others.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He never thought.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he could get the biggest job in any Russian brigade and be a big shot, and be a commander.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he wanted-- that's what he promised the people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's what he wanted to accomplish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the winter, they used to prepare a lot more.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very hard, because the Germans found out that the peasants are giving food to the partisans too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- and they restricted that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So sometimes you had to-- to take food by force.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they, for the winter, they prepared-- before we settled down, and we got to be what we were, it was not easy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And only the youngsters, the younger people, very brave people-- they loved my husband.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They obeyed every rule and regulation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One thing he was screaming always-- if we won't have a discipline, we won't have any-- we won't survive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There is-- with Jews, it's very hard to manage, because we have different opinions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have different ideas.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And each one wants to be a commander.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tremendously-- just by love and devotion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He knew how to talk to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I won't say that not once he had to raise his voice and say something what he wasn't supposed to say, but when he spoke or when he asked, it was like you could hear a fly passing by.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The respect and the love to him was incredible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was like God.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If somebody said, if they'll go, and by him, they'll survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If he won't be on the base and something will happen, we won't survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's how people believed in him-- like in God.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was '42--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
